`podman top` ignores ps OPTIONS:
```go
libpod/container_top.go
       // [...] We believe that
       // writing a go library which parses procFS in a ps-compatible way may
       // be more beneficial in the long run.  Until then, args will be
       // ignored.
```
This is a simple reminder so the issue is not forgotten.

(And ITM someone might want to upodate the man page, especially if the fix will take a long time)
